means: (用于表示惊讶、震惊或厌烦，可能具冒犯意味)天哪，哎呀

value.def: Jesus or Jesus Christ is the name of the man who Christians believe was the son of God, and whose teachings are the basis of Christianity.
Jesus is used by some people to express surprise, shock, or annoyance. This use could cause offence.
value.tran: （用于表示惊讶、震惊或厌烦，可能具冒犯意味）天哪，哎呀
